txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the Men and Wood-trolls surrounding the outpost of Gwingris. You can return the items to Maedlathron at Gwingris in Eregion for reward.
'This is a good thing you have done. Thank you.'
'The Men to the east are here at the behest of our enemies...bring the fight to them and return with proof of their defeat. We should also take the broken weapons from the Wood-trolls.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Broken Wooden Clubs
Maedlathron awaits the return of a collection of broken wooden clubs at the Elf-encampment at Gwingris.
Deliver the broken wood clubs to Maedlathron in Gwingris within Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver broken wooden clubs from the Men and Wood-trolls near and surrounding the Elf-encampment of Gwingris to the Elf Maedlathron.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the Men and Wood-trolls surrounding the outpost of Gwingris.
